      <div class="lg:col-span-7">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">The Passenger Experience</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-500 mb-8">
          A world-class UX designed to make booking a ride as simple as 2 taps. Optimized for African network conditions.
        </p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div>
