             <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Users can book a ride for later. Great for airport transfers and early morning commutes.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
             <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Real-Time Chat</h4>
             <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">In-app chat and VoIP calling to driver (masking phone numbers for privacy).</p>
          </div>
          <div>
